# Project Structure

This project uses Next.js App Router and Supabase. Start here to understand the layout.

- Root config
    - [package.json](mdc:package.json)
    - [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
    - [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs)
    - [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts)
    - [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs)
    - [bun.lock](mdc:bun.lock)

- App Router (pages, layouts, loading)
    - Root layout: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)
    - Root loading: [src/app/loading.tsx](mdc:src/app/loading.tsx)
    - Auth group: [src/app/(auth)/](<mdc:src/app/(auth)/>)
        - Layout: [src/app/(auth)/layout.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(auth)/layout.tsx>)
        - Login: [src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx>)
        - Register: [src/app/(auth)/register/page.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(auth)/register/page.tsx>)
    - Main group: [src/app/(main)/](<mdc:src/app/(main)/>)
        - Layout: [src/app/(main)/layout.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(main)/layout.tsx>)
        - Dashboard group: [src/app/(main)/(dashboard)/](<mdc:src/app/(main)/(dashboard)/>)
            - Layout: [src/app/(main)/(dashboard)/layout.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(main)/(dashboard)/layout.tsx>)
            - Page: [src/app/(main)/(dashboard)/page.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(main)/(dashboard)/page.tsx>)
        - Retro group: [src/app/(main)/(retro)/retro/[id]/](<mdc:src/app/(main)/(retro)/retro/[id]/>)
            - Page: [src/app/(main)/(retro)/retro/[id]/page.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(main)/(retro)/retro/[id]/page.tsx>)
            - Loading/NotFound: [loading.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(main)/(retro)/retro/[id]/loading.tsx>), [not-found.tsx](<mdc:src/app/(main)/(retro)/retro/[id]/not-found.tsx>)

- Middleware (route protection and redirects)
    - [src/middleware.ts](mdc:src/middleware.ts)

- Supabase (client, server, schema)
    - [src/lib/supabase/client.ts](mdc:src/lib/supabase/client.ts)
    - [src/lib/supabase/server.ts](mdc:src/lib/supabase/server.ts)
    - [src/lib/supabase/schema.ts](mdc:src/lib/supabase/schema.ts)

- Actions (server actions)
    - Auth: [src/actions/auth.ts](mdc:src/actions/auth.ts)
    - Retro: [src/actions/retro.ts](mdc:src/actions/retro.ts)

- Queries (client hooks, mutations)
    - Auth: [src/queries/auth.ts](mdc:src/queries/auth.ts)
    - Retro: [src/queries/retro.ts](mdc:src/queries/retro.ts)

- Context Providers
    - Auth: [src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx)
    - Retro: [src/contexts/RetroContext.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/RetroContext.tsx)

- Layout components
    - Providers: [src/components/Layouts/ProvidersRootLayout.tsx](mdc:src/components/Layouts/ProvidersRootLayout.tsx), [src/components/Layouts/ProvidersMainLayout.tsx](mdc:src/components/Layouts/ProvidersMainLayout.tsx)
    - Main Layout UI: [src/components/Layouts/Main/](mdc:src/components/Layouts/Main/)

- UI primitives and shared components
    - UI: [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui/)
    - Shared Form: [src/components/Shared/Form/](mdc:src/components/Shared/Form/)

- Retro domain components
    - [src/components/Retro/](mdc:src/components/Retro/)
    - Retro Create: [src/components/RetroCreate/](mdc:src/components/RetroCreate/)

- Styles and public assets
    - Global CSS: [src/styles/globals.css](mdc:src/styles/globals.css)
    - Public assets: [public/](mdc:public/)

